title: Sooooo?
body: A few days away from new season opening and I still cant transfer to my home region this is fucking saaaaaaaad.

replies.body: Hollymonster was able to update people not too long ago, but it does still seem like it'll take a little while. She mentioned in [**her update**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/rlu6awv4-transfer-service-update) that it should be late Jan/early Feb, and there should be some type of discount as well.
